stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Active

    state Active {
        [*] --> NumLockOff
        NumLockOff --> NumLockOn : NumLock pressed
        NumLockOn --> NumLockOff : NumLock pressed
        --
        [*] --> CapsLockOff
        CapsLockOff --> CapsLockOn : CapsLock pressed
        CapsLockOn --> CapsLockOff : CapsLock pressed
        --
        [*] --> ScrollLockOff
        ScrollLockOff --> ScrollLockOn : ScrollLock pressed
        ScrollLockOn --> ScrollLockOff : ScrollLock pressed
    }

    Active --> [*] : power off

    note left of Active
        Three independent regions
        run concurrently while the
        keyboard is powered on.
    end note
